      "You are all welcome to join us.  It seems we have quite a little group 
forming.  And yet we have no mission.  We are wanderers.  is there somewhere 
you would like us to take you."  He looked at each of them in turn ending 
with the little one by Trinity.  "We welcome all people regardless of their 
past."
